WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:19.260
Imagine, if you will -- a gift.

00:00:20.260 --> 00:00:23.260
I'd like for you to picture it in your mind.

00:00:23.260 --> 00:00:25.260
It's not too big --

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:27.260
about the size of a golf ball.

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:30.260
So envision what it looks like all wrapped up.

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:33.260
But before I show you what's inside,

00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:36.260
I will tell you, it's going to do incredible things for you.

00:00:36.260 --> 00:00:39.260
It will bring all of your family together.

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:43.260
You will feel loved and appreciated like never before

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:45.260
and reconnect with friends and acquaintances

00:00:45.260 --> 00:00:47.260
you haven't heard from in years.

00:00:47.260 --> 00:00:49.260
Adoration and admiration

00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:52.260
will overwhelm you.

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:55.260
It will recalibrate what's most important in your life.

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:57.260
It will redefine your sense

00:00:57.260 --> 00:01:00.260
of spirituality and faith.

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:02.260
You'll have a new understanding

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:04.260
and trust in your body.

00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:07.260
You'll have unsurpassed vitality and energy.

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:09.260
You'll expand your vocabulary,

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:11.260
meet new people,

00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:14.260
and you'll have a healthier lifestyle.

00:01:14.260 --> 00:01:16.260
And get this --

00:01:16.260 --> 00:01:18.260
you'll have an eight-week vacation

00:01:18.260 --> 00:01:21.260
of doing absolutely nothing.

00:01:21.260 --> 00:01:24.260
You'll eat countless gourmet meals.

00:01:24.260 --> 00:01:27.260
Flowers will arrive by the truckload.

00:01:27.260 --> 00:01:29.260
People will say to you,

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:32.260
"You look great. Have you had any work done?"

00:01:32.260 --> 00:01:34.260
And you'll have a lifetime supply

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:37.260
of good drugs.

00:01:37.260 --> 00:01:40.260
You'll be challenged, inspired,

00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:43.260
motivated and humbled.

00:01:43.260 --> 00:01:46.260
Your life will have new meaning.

00:01:46.260 --> 00:01:48.260
Peace, health,

00:01:48.260 --> 00:01:51.260
serenity, happiness,

00:01:51.260 --> 00:01:53.260
nirvana.

00:01:53.260 --> 00:01:55.260
The price?

00:01:55.260 --> 00:01:58.260
$55,000,

00:01:58.260 --> 00:02:01.260
and that's an incredible deal.

00:02:01.260 --> 00:02:03.260
By now I know you're dying to know

00:02:03.260 --> 00:02:06.260
what it is and where you can get one.

00:02:06.260 --> 00:02:08.260
Does Amazon carry it?

00:02:08.260 --> 00:02:10.260
Does it have the Apple logo on it?

00:02:10.260 --> 00:02:13.260
Is there a waiting list?

00:02:13.260 --> 00:02:15.260
Not likely.

00:02:15.260 --> 00:02:18.260
This gift came to me about five months ago.

00:02:18.260 --> 00:02:20.260
It looked more like this when it was all wrapped up --

00:02:20.260 --> 00:02:22.260
not quite so pretty.

00:02:23.260 --> 00:02:25.260
And this,

00:02:26.260 --> 00:02:29.260
and then this.

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:31.260
It was a rare gem --

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:33.260
a brain tumor,

00:02:33.260 --> 00:02:36.260
hemangioblastoma --

00:02:36.260 --> 00:02:39.260
the gift that keeps on giving.

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:41.260
And while I'm okay now,

00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:43.260
I wouldn't wish this gift for you.

00:02:43.260 --> 00:02:45.260
I'm not sure you'd want it.

00:02:45.260 --> 00:02:48.260
But I wouldn't change my experience.

00:02:48.260 --> 00:02:51.260
It profoundly altered my life

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:53.260
in ways I didn't expect

00:02:53.260 --> 00:02:55.260
in all the ways I just shared with you.

00:02:55.260 --> 00:02:57.260
So the next time you're faced

00:02:57.260 --> 00:03:00.260
with something that's unexpected,

00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:03.260
unwanted and uncertain,

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:05.260
consider

00:03:05.260 --> 00:03:08.260
that it just may be a gift.

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:11.260
(Applause)

